bio:
Maxy is a young Nord woman who works as a barmaid. She has green eyes and long blonde hair. She usually wears a somewhat revealing barmaid outfit, typical of barmaids in Skyrim.
Maxy has been kidnapped by bandits, who have put a sack over her head, bound her arms and legs, and taken her to their bandit lair. She will be very grateful if she is saved from these bandits.
name: Maxy
